Don't waste your time--followed the recipe with the exception of using panko (japanese bread crumbs) versus traditional breadcrumbs--and I can't remember a recipe that I like less.

Rating: 2
At the advice of previous reviewers I jazzed this up alot. Added garlic & salt to the buttermilk & let it marinate for 2 hours. Also added extra spices to the crust. It still was pretty boring. Not bad, just ho-hum. Plenty of better low fat ways to prepare chicken. Oh-the lemon zest was nice.

